{"tid":702543,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"孫悟空拍極唔完　周星馳落實搞「西遊」動畫","createTime":"2018-06-15T03:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T09:06:50.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c88bf554e6ebcc0dd165482a1ed52f614b911f8","tid":702543,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"居幕後多年嘅周星馳，依家鮮有出鏡，不過佢嘅「拿手好戲」改編經典故仔《西遊記》就好似拍極唔完，繼《大話西遊之月光寶盒》、《大話西遊之仙履奇緣》、《西遊．降魔篇》及《西遊伏妖篇》之後，佢又着手搞「西遊」片。 <br />\n<br />\n據內地傳媒消息指，在法國安錫國際動畫節活動期間，東方夢工廠首席創意官周珮鈴宣布周星馳已確定參與東方夢工廠全新動畫電影專案The Monkey King（暫譯：齊天大聖）的創意開發，雙方將一起打造動畫作品。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180615/mobile/bkn-20180615101003858-0615_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180615%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180615101003858-0615_00862_001.html&d=pJmRmfFXVjkpliUNsRgPq5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2f827937\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180615/mobile/bkn-20180615101003858-0615_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d7219a8ce0d70d31576ee70c9fe74bdc06317513","tid":702543,"uid":100150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"諗極都唔明，點解年年賀歲片都要拍西遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有諗過係支那多多限制，不過唔明點解四大名著剩係拍西遊記唔拍水滸傳嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359ef7479e7c17a06f1ba9c23789ce24260266dd","tid":702543,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:09:29.000Z","msg":"支那唔係要禁呢d題材?"},{"pid":"6735d179393989bd0504871e8681bf4c78414cba","tid":702543,"uid":127272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:10:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那得隻馬嬲可以打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8035da3a165f094b7637f399c2d6db3e766d673b","tid":702543,"uid":70846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7219a8ce0d70d31576ee70c9fe74bdc0631751